rComments: Éric (appellez-lui par son prénom) est un prof fantastique. Ces cours sont intéressant, même s'ils étaient à 19h le soir. Le "test" de mi-session est facile si tu as pris des notes lors du semestre et que tu écoutes en classe. Deux projets d'équipe qui ne sont pas super difficile, mais assurez vous d'avoir de bons coéquipiers.
teacherRatingTags: ['Clear grading criteria', 'Gives good feedback', 'Accessible outside class']

rComments: he is just great! Amazing class and super easy A.

Eric is unclear with his assignments and unreceptive to criticism and concerns about the teaching of his course. His lectures are just summaries of the readings, and he marks participation even though there is little chance to actively participate other than in discussions about the readings. Don't listen to the other reviews - not the best prof!

10/10 recommend! Super chill and easy going, really want his student to succeed and purposefully makes the midterm very easy. 2 group video projects and 2 papers to go along with them. No final exam! Super fun and funny guy

The cool uncle you always wanted. Will teach class barefoot. Fashion sense will leave you SHOOK. Easy projects, easy exam. Will spend an entire class watching Super Bowl commercials. 10/10 would recommend.

By far the best prof at uottawa. Sometimes teaches class barefoot? Best fashion sense. Sometimes blasts the Game of Thrones soundtrack as students enter? Probably sits alone in the dark at 3am coming up with conspiracy theories. Would definitely recommend. Over all cool guy.
